---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout title="About" authorName="About">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <header>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6 sm:text-5xl">About</h1>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          I like automating tasks and organizing data.
        </p>
        <p class="text-md text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          I view software and data engineering as the ultimate tools for organization. Whether I'm building 
          API pipelines at work or tier-listing my <a href="https://me-db.app/user/e_lee538" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">personal media collection</a> with <a href="/projects/me-db">ME-DB</a>, <b>I strive to create code to
          automate the collection of useful data and deliver information in a clear interface.</b>
        </p>
        <p class="text-md text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Python is my language of choice and I've used it extensively over the past 5 years to analyze data, build a web app, and automate several routine tasks. 
          I also have experience developing with JavaScript, Salesforce Apex, and Microsoft Power Platform.
          Currently, I'm learning data warehouse management and utilizing AI & LLMs within the Azure ecosystem.
        </p>
        <p class="text-md text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          In my free time, I enjoy <a href="/about/personal">playing sports</a>, <a href="/music">making music</a>, and <a href="https://me-db.app/user/Ethan/sandwiches" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">eating sandwiches</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Key Values -->
    <section class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-4">Key Values</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {['Team Building', 'Expressive Communication', 'Creative Ideas', 'Top-Down Planning'].map((value) => (
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 rounded-full font-bold text-xs border border-blue-100 shadow-sm transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:bg-blue-100">
            {value}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</ContentLayout>
